---
import BaseLayout from "@layouts/BaseLayout.astro";

const pageTitle = "國史年表｜香港共和國";
const pageDescription =
  "香港共和國國史年表：重大事件與官方紀錄（按日期排列）。";
---

<BaseLayout title={pageTitle} description={pageDescription}>
  <section class="head">
    <div class="badge">國史檔案</div>
    <h1>國史年表</h1>
    <p class="lead">
      本頁列示香港共和國重大事件之官方紀錄（概述）。日期以公曆表示；如有版本差異，
      以政府正式登載之文件與公報版本為準。
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="archive">
    <div class="archive-head">
      <h2>主要里程碑</h2>
      <div class="meta">更新：按需增補</div>
    </div>

    <div class="timeline" role="list">
      <div class="entry" role="listitem">
        <div class="date">
          <div class="ymd">2043-07-01</div>
          <div class="label">制度運作</div>
        </div>

        <div class="body">
          <h3>共和國制度開始運作</h3>
          <p>
            憲政治理開始運作；公共機構依法履行職權，確保公共服務、司法程序與行政運作之連續性。
          </p>
          <div class="tags">
            <span class="tag">憲政</span>
            <span class="tag">公共服務</span>
            <span class="tag">機關運作</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="entry" role="listitem">
        <div class="date">
          <div class="ymd">2043-07-15</div>
          <div class="label">金融與市場</div>
        </div>

        <div class="body">
          <h3>金融連續性安排正式確認</h3>
          <p>
            市場結算、合約連續性及金融系統運作安排獲正式確認，並向市場及公共機構發布實施指引。
          </p>
          <div class="tags">
            <span class="tag">金融穩定</span>
            <span class="tag">結算</span>
            <span class="tag">市場秩序</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="entry" role="listitem">
        <div class="date">
          <div class="ymd">2043-08-03</div>
          <div class="label">司法</div>
        </div>

        <div class="body">
          <h3>法院行政與司法制度安排</h3>
          <p>
            司法行政架構與法院運作安排完成調整，並重申司法獨立與正當程序保障，確保審判秩序與
            法律救濟可及性。
          </p>
          <div class="tags">
            <span class="tag">司法獨立</span>
            <span class="tag">程序正義</span>
            <span class="tag">法院行政</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="note">
      提示：下一步可將年表事件拆分為可引用之檔案條目（具永久連結與引用格式），並接入公告或公報之對應文件。
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="links">
    <a class="link" href="/HKR/press">
      <span class="l-title">前往公告中心</span>
      <span class="l-desc">查閱政策發布、聲明與新聞稿</span>
    </a>
    <a class="link" href="/HKR/laws">
      <span class="l-title">查閱法律入口</span>
      <span class="l-desc">憲政框架與核心法規概述</span>
    </a>
    <a class="link" href="/HKR/government">
      <span class="l-title">政府架構</span>
      <span class="l-desc">憲制機關與公共機構</span>
    </a>
  </section>

  <style>
    .head {
      padding-top: 0.25rem;
    }

    .badge {
      display: inline-block;
      font-size: 0.85rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.8px;
      color: #fff;
      background: #b80000;
      padding: 0.25rem 0.55rem;
      border-radius: 999px;
      margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    }

    .lead {
      color: #444;
      font-size: 1.05rem;
      max-width: 60rem;
    }

    .archive {
      margin-top: 1.8rem;
      border: 1px solid #e7e7e7;
      border-radius: 18px;
      overflow: hidden;
      background: #fff;
    }

    .archive-head {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: baseline;
      gap: 1rem;
      padding: 1rem 1rem 0.85rem;
      background: #fafafa;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #eeeeee;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }

    .archive-head h2 {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 1.25rem;
    }

    .meta {
      color: #666;
      font-size: 0.92rem;
      white-space: nowrap;
    }

    .timeline {
      padding: 0.2rem 0;
    }

    .entry {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 170px 1fr;
      gap: 1rem;
      padding: 1rem;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #eeeeee;
      position: relative;
    }

    .entry:last-child {
      border-bottom: none;
    }

    .date {
      border-right: 2px solid #f0f0f0;
      padding-right: 1rem;
    }

    .ymd {
      font-weight: 900;
      color: #111;
      font-size: 0.98rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.2px;
    }

    .label {
      margin-top: 0.35rem;
      display: inline-flex;
      width: fit-content;
      padding: 0.18rem 0.55rem;
      border-radius: 999px;
      border: 1px solid #e7e7e7;
      background: #fafafa;
      color: #333;
      font-weight: 800;
      font-size: 0.85rem;
    }

    .body h3 {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 1.08rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.2px;
    }

    .body p {
      margin: 0.35rem 0 0;
      color: #444;
    }

    .tags {
      margin-top: 0.7rem;
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 0.45rem;
    }

    .tag {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      padding: 0.16rem 0.5rem;
      border-radius: 999px;
      border: 1px solid #e7e7e7;
      background: #fff;
      color: #333;
      font-weight: 750;
      font-size: 0.84rem;
    }

    .note {
      padding: 0.9rem 1rem;
      color: #666;
      background: #fafafa;
      border-top: 1px solid #eeeeee;
      font-size: 0.92rem;
    }

    .links {
      margin-top: 1.5rem;
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr));
      gap: 1rem;
    }

    .link {
      display: block;
      border: 1px solid #e7e7e7;
      border-radius: 16px;
      background: #fafafa;
      padding: 1rem;
      text-decoration: none;
      color: #111;
    }

    .link:hover {
      border-color: #b80000;
      background: #fff;
      box-shadow: 0 10px 26px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06);
    }

    .l-title {
      display: block;
      font-weight: 900;
      margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
    }

    .l-desc {
      display: block;
      color: #555;
      font-size: 0.95rem;
    }

    @media (max-width: 980px) {
      .entry {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }
      .date {
        border-right: none;
        padding-right: 0;
      }
      .links {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }
    }
  </style>
</BaseLayout>
